    • Animal

      public Animal(Location location, int BREEDING_AGE, int MAX_AGE, double BREEDING_PROBABILITY, int MAX_LITTER_SIZE, boolean infected)
      Create a new prey animal.
      Parameters:
      location - The location within the field.
      BREEDING_AGE - The age at which this type of prey can breed
      MAX_AGE - The maximum age that this prey can live too.
      BREEDING_PROBABILITY - The probability of this type of prey breeding
      MAX_LITTER_SIZE - The maximum number of prey this type of prey will give birth too
